INSERT INTO `zuk_article` VALUES ('37', '1', '84', 'Moto M 天声 锋芒', 'Moto, 桌面, 指纹识别, 锁屏', '', '0', '                            	                            	<div class=\"viewthread_content\" author=\"静爱与静界\" pid=\"4208412\" formhash=\"28977099\">\r\n\r\n<div class=\"viewthread_table\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\"><tbody><tr><td id=\"postmessage_4208412\"><br>\r\n上手Moto M，会带来一种“扎实”感，当然或许这样的感觉只有拿到手上的时候才能明显感觉到，与之前Moto系列的很多产品不同的是，Moto M采用了全金属机身的设计，这样的材质使用在近几代Moto产品上并不多见，“扎实”感便由此而来，而除了我们拿到的金色版之外，Moto M还提供银色版供选择。<br>\r\n\r\n<ignore_js_op>\r\n\r\n<img style=\"cursor:pointer\" id=\"aimg_275631\" aid=\"275631\" src=\"http://img.bbs.lenovomobile.cn/forum/201611/09/215837tpdk5dez52nnk2ks.png.thumb.jpg\" onclick=\"zoom(this, this.getAttribute(\'zoomfile\'), 0, 0, \'1\')\" zoomfile=\"http://img.bbs.lenovomobile.cn/forum/201611/09/215837tpdk5dez52nnk2ks.png\" file=\"http://img.bbs.lenovomobile.cn/forum/201611/09/215837tpdk5dez52nnk2ks.png.thumb.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" onmouseover=\"showMenu({\'ctrlid\':this.id,\'pos\':\'12\'})\">\r\n\r\n<div class=\"tip tip_4 aimg_tip\" style=\"position: absolute; display: none\" disautofocus=\"true\">\r\n<div class=\"xs0\">\r\n<p><strong>JUXA$Q75BBNQ19%]T4$EG@1.png</strong></p>\r\n<p>\r\n\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"xg1\"><span class=\"y xg1\"><span title=\"2016-11-9 21:58\">6 天前</span> 上传</span><em>490.68 KB</em></p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"tip_horn\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n</ignore_js_op>\r\n<br>\r\nMoto M依然是漂亮的金属机身，只不过机身圆角更大，看起来更加圆润优雅。正面除了下巴位置Moto的标志以外别无他物，简洁的不得了。<a href=\"http://bbs.zuk.cn/z1/t15887/\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"relatedlink\">指纹</a>识别不出意料的被放置在了手机后方，比较遗憾的是经典的Moto Logo没有放在中间。<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\r\n<ignore_js_op>\r\n\r\n<img style=\"cursor:pointer\" id=\"aimg_275641\" aid=\"275641\" src=\"http://img.bbs.lenovomobile.cn/forum/201611/09/220049grr3z4n0ww9r4ii4.png.thumb.jpg\" onclick=\"zoom(this, this.getAttribute(\'zoomfile\'), 0, 0, \'1\')\" zoomfile=\"http://img.bbs.lenovomobile.cn/forum/201611/09/220049grr3z4n0ww9r4ii4.png\" file=\"http://img.bbs.lenovomobile.cn/forum/201611/09/220049grr3z4n0ww9r4ii4.png.thumb.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" onmouseover=\"showMenu({\'ctrlid\':this.id,\'pos\':\'12\'})\">\r\n\r\n<div class=\"tip tip_4 aimg_tip\" style=\"position: absolute; display: none\" disautofocus=\"true\">\r\n<div class=\"xs0\">\r\n<p><strong>)]JZ3`4JS$_B_3ZH@RCJ)G4.png</strong></p>\r\n<p>\r\n\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"xg1\"><span class=\"y xg1\"><span title=\"2016-11-9 22:00\">6 天前</span> 上传</span><em>451.63 KB</em></p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"tip_horn\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n</ignore_js_op>\r\n<br>\r\nMoto M是Moto旗下为数不多的采用了全金属机身设计的产品，同时应用了锆英砂喷砂技术处理，使表面具有耐磨、抗腐蚀等特性。Moto M在表面采用了纳米涂层，能够抵御一般的泼溅、淋雨。<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\r\n<ignore_js_op>\r\n\r\n<img style=\"cursor:pointer\" id=\"aimg_275618\" aid=\"275618\" src=\"http://img.bbs.lenovomobile.cn/forum/201611/09/215236nb19bbulb4jjzh41.jpg.thumb.jpg\" onclick=\"zoom(this, this.getAttribute(\'zoomfile\'), 0, 0, \'1\')\" zoomfile=\"http://img.bbs.lenovomobile.cn/forum/201611/09/215236nb19bbulb4jjzh41.jpg\" file=\"http://img.bbs.lenovomobile.cn/forum/201611/09/215236nb19bbulb4jjzh41.jpg.thumb.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" onmouseover=\"showMenu({\'ctrlid\':this.id,\'pos\':\'12\'})\">\r\n\r\n<div class=\"tip tip_4 aimg_tip\" style=\"position: absolute; display: none\" disautofocus=\"true\">\r\n<div class=\"xs0\">\r\n<p><strong>Moto M_M_FPS_HomeLock_DS_Port_APAC_SC.jpg</strong></p>\r\n<p>\r\n\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"xg1\"><span class=\"y xg1\"><span title=\"2016-11-9 21:52\">6 天前</span> 上传</span><em>1.29 MB</em></p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"tip_horn\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n</ignore_js_op>\r\n<br>\r\n锁屏界面很清新，给人一种清静，心旷神怡。<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\r\n<ignore_js_op>\r\n\r\n<img style=\"cursor:pointer\" id=\"aimg_275619\" aid=\"275619\" src=\"http://img.bbs.lenovomobile.cn/forum/201611/09/215247q8a6qa8taqo7qz6t.jpg.thumb.jpg\" onclick=\"zoom(this, this.getAttribute(\'zoomfile\'), 0, 0, \'1\')\" zoomfile=\"http://img.bbs.lenovomobile.cn/forum/201611/09/215247q8a6qa