INSERT INTO `zuk_article` VALUES ('212', '1', '106', '三分钟教你从屌丝变身专业摄影师（色影师）的7种拍照神', '拍照, 相机, 光圈, 社交网络, 朋友圈', '/Uploads/thumbnail/2016/11/23/5835ae0ade6d4.jpg', '0', '<div class=\"viewthread_content\">\r\n	<div class=\"viewthread_table\">\r\n		<table cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n			<tbody>\r\n				<tr>\r\n					<td id=\"postmessage_4170086\">\r\n						<i class=\"pstatus\"> 本帖最后由 小小康 于 2016-11-6 19:19 编辑 </i><br />\r\n						<div align=\"center\">\r\n							<span><span><span><span style=\"background-color:#FF00FF;\">为什么你发朋友圈儿的照片好友都不喜欢点赞？</span></span></span></span>\r\n						</div>\r\n<br />\r\n<span><span>\r\n						<div align=\"center\">\r\n							<img smilieid=\"96\" src=\"static/image/smiley/shenqidabai/01.gif\" &nbsp;&nbsp;border=\"0\" alt=\"\">\r\n						</div>\r\n<br />\r\n<span>\r\n						<div align=\"center\">\r\n							<span>为什么处心积虑给女神的拍的照片不能换来一声 么么哒</span><img smilieid=\"108\" src=\"static/image/smiley/shenqidabai/20.gif\" &nbsp;&nbsp;border=\"0\" alt=\"\">\r\n						</div>\r\n</span></span></span><span><span><span><br />\r\n</span><span><br />\r\n						<div align=\"center\">\r\n							<span>为什么别人发在社交<a href=\"http://bbs.zuk.cn/z1/t28005/\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"relatedlink\">网络</a>里的照片都辣麽好看？？？</span>\r\n						</div>\r\n<br />\r\n</span><span><br />\r\n						<div align=\"center\">\r\n							<span>表急，今天本老司机来拯救你们！</span><img smilieid=\"103\" src=\"static/image/smiley/shenqidabai/15.gif\" &nbsp;&nbsp;border=\"0\" alt=\"\">\r\n						</div>\r\n<br />\r\n</span><span><br />\r\n						<div align=\"center\">\r\n							<span>作为一条单身狗，每天遭受9个小时以上的拍打喂食早已是家常便饭，肉体一直处于旅行无能的状态，</span>\r\n						</div>\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n						<div align=\"center\">\r\n							<span>所以本大编会很珍惜每一次的出游，从260万像素卡片机入门，到APS-C再到全画幅单反，一直到近期变身手机摄影党，啪照是从小鲜肉变身怪大叔这么多年间始终没有改变的爱好。</span>\r\n						</div>\r\n</span><span>&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; </span></span></span><img smilieid=\"99\" src=\"static/image/smiley/shenqidabai/24.gif\" &nbsp;&nbsp;border=\"0\" alt=\"\"><span><span><span><br />\r\n						<div align=\"center\">\r\n							<span>这篇，就让我们来聊聊那些构图的秘密。</span>\r\n						</div>\r\n<br />\r\n</span></span></span><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n						<div align=\"center\">\r\n							<span><span><span>三角形构图法：让背景中的元素成为最佳拍档</span></span></span>\r\n						</div>\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span><span><span>三角形构图法又名黄金分割构图法，是摄影最为经典的构图方法之一，通常由人和背景共同构成三角形形状，增强画面的稳定感和协调性。</span></span></span><span><span><span><br />\r\n我们不必拘泥于三角形的角度或周长，只要找到拍照时适合做搭档的那几个背景元素</span></span></span> <img id=\"aimg_273987\" src=\"http://img.bbs.lenovomobile.cn/forum/201611/06/191331zd22xxlybfs8iszy.jpg.thumb.jpg\" /> \r\n						<div class=\"tip tip_4 aimg_tip\">\r\n							<div class=\"xs0\">\r\n								<p>\r\n									<strong>1.jpg</strong>\r\n								</p>\r\n								<p>\r\n									<br />\r\n								</p>\r\n								<p class=\"xg1\">\r\n									<span class=\"y xg1\">2016-11-6 19:13 上传</span><em>43.8 KB</em>\r\n								</p>\r\n							</div>\r\n							<div class=\"tip_horn\">\r\n							</div>\r\n						</div>\r\n<span><br />\r\n</span><br />\r\n<span><span><span>可能是家具，电器，装饰陈设，甚至沙发也是可以的。</span></span></span><br />\r\n<img id=\"aimg_273988\" src=\"http://img.bbs.lenovomobile.cn/forum/201611/06/191331dcmtcoatak80eow8.jpg.thumb.jpg\" /> \r\n						<div class=\"tip tip_4 aimg_tip\">\r\n							<div class=\"xs0\">\r\n								<p>\r\n									<strong>2.jpg</strong>\r\n								</p>\r\n								<p>\r\n									<br />\r\n								</p>\r\n								<p class=\"xg1\">\r\n									<span class=\"y xg1\">2016-11-6 19:13 上传</span><em>33.77 KB</em>\r\n								</p>\r\n							</div>\r\n							<div class=\"tip_horn\">\r\n							</div>\r\n						</div>\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span><span><span>想看更多？回个帖子，你不会怀孕的！回个帖子，你不会怀孕的！回个帖子，你不会怀孕的！</span></span></span><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span><span><span>举手之劳就能鼓励楼主的事儿说三遍！</span><img smilieid=\"104\" src=\"static/image/smiley/shenqidabai/13.gif\" &nbsp;&nbsp;border=\"0\" alt=\"\"></span></span><br />\r\n<span><span>\r\n						<div align=\"center\">\r\n							井字构图法：视觉的黄金比例\r\n						</div>\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span>也叫三分构图法，顾名思义，按照长度和宽度三等分的比例划分，拍摄时将人脸或者被摄物置于长度和宽度三等分的四个交界点。这种构图方法如同数学中的黄金比例一般，呈现完美结构，也是最经典的摄影构图方法。</span><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span>图3&nbsp;&nbsp;横图的井字：焦点在画面中央的偏左或偏右，三分线的构图带来了视觉的延伸性</span><br />\r\n<img id=\"aimg_273989\" src=\"http://img.bbs.lenovomobile.cn/forum/201611/06/191332l9wialdgxgw9edwe.jpg.thumb.jpg\" /> \r\n						<div class=\"tip tip_4 aimg_tip\">\r\n							<div class=\"xs0\">\r\n								<p>\r\n									<strong>3.jpg</strong>\r\n								</p>\r\n								<p>\r\n									<br />\r\n								</p>\r\n								<p class=\"xg1\">\r\n									<span class=\"y xg1\">2016-11-6 19:13 上传</span><em>41.2 KB</em>\r\n								</p>\r\n							</div>\r\n							<div class=\"tip_horn\">\r\n							</div>\r\n						</div>\r\n<br />\r\n<span><br />\r\n图4&nbsp;&nbsp;竖图的井字： “靠边站”，更有意境。</span><br />\r\n<img id=\"aimg_273990\" src=\"http://img.bbs.lenovomobile.cn/forum/201611/06/191332yhbmh3b4jmh0lr50.jpg.thumb.jpg\" /> \r\n						<div class=\"tip tip_4 aimg_tip\">\r\n							<div class=\"xs0\">\r\n								<p>\r\n									<strong>4.jpg</strong>\r\n								</p>\r\n								<p>\r\n									<br />\r\n								</p>\r\n								<p class=\"xg1\">\r\n									<span class=\"y xg1\">2016-11-6 19:13 上传</span><em>91.09 KB</em>\r\n								</p>\r\n							</div>\r\n							<div class=\"tip_horn\">\r\n							</div>\r\n						</div>\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n						<div align=\"center\">\r\n							<span>中央构图法：我就是主角</span>\r\n						</div>\r\n<br />\r\n						<div align=\"center\">\r\n							<span><br />\r\n</span>\r\n						</div>\r\n<br />\r\n<span>顾名思义，把人物位于照片的中线拍摄，称为中央构图。<br />\r\n中央构图法的难点在于容易把照片拍的平淡，变成一张傻乎乎的游客照。所以，格局对于背景的要求格外高：简单明朗的对称结构，或者易于突出人物的简洁背景。</span><br />\r\n<img id=\"aimg_273999\" src=\"http://img.bbs.lenovomobile.cn/forum/201611/06/191344nu1vlgrr97el7eqg.jpg.thumb.jpg\" /> \r\n						<div class=\"tip tip_4 aimg_tip\">\r\n							<div class=\"xs0\">\r\n								<p>\r\n									<strong>5.jpg</strong>\r\n								</p>\r\n								<p>\r\n									<br />\r\n								</p>\r\n								<p class=\"xg1\">\r\n									<span class=\"y xg1\">2016-11-6 19:13 上传</span><em>57.25 KB</em>\r\n								</p>\r\n							</div>\r\n							<div class=\"tip_horn\">\r\n							</div>\r\n						</div>\r\n<span><br />\r\n<br />\r\n人像在照片中央，不会让背景喧宾夺主，这种拍摄手法百搭而又不失优雅</span><br />\r\n<img id=\"aimg_274000\" src=\"http://img.bbs.lenovomobile.cn/forum/201611/06/191345wq386kj615d11zqz.jpg.thumb.jpg\" /> \r\n						<div class=\"tip tip_4 aimg_tip\">\r\n							<div class=\"xs0\">\r\n								<p>\r\n									<strong>6.jpg</strong>\r\n								</p>\r\n								<p>\r\n									<br />\r\n								</p>\r\n								<p class=\"xg1\">\r\n									<span class=\"y xg1\">2016-11-6 19:13 上传</span><em>158.41 KB</em>\r\n								</p>\r\n							</div>\r\n							<div class=\"tip_horn\">\r\n							</div>\r\n						</div>\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n						<div align=\"center\">\r\n							对角线构图法：灵动之美\r\n						</div>\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span>对角线构图法是在拍摄时人物运用一定角度的斜拍，</span><br />\r\n<span>这样的画面相，比直线拍摄增添了动感和活力，也吸引眼球。<br />\r\n45度角的准斜线拍摄，具有拉长线条的效果，大长腿靠先天优势也要靠技术</span><br />\r\n<span><br />\r\n</span> <img id=\"aimg_273991\" src=\"http://img.bbs.lenovomobile.cn/forum/201611/06/191333ulrygystkywyturs.jpg.thumb.jpg\" /> \r\n						<div class=\"tip tip_4 aimg_tip\">\r\n							<div class=\"xs0\">\r\n								<p>\r\n									<strong>5.jpg</strong>\r\n								</p>\r\n								<p>\r\n									<br />\r\n								</p>\r\n								<p class=\"xg1\">\r\n									<span class=\"y xg1\">2016-11-6 19:13 上传</span><em>54.15 KB</em>\r\n								</p>\r\n							</div>\r\n							<div class=\"tip_horn\">\r\n							</div>\r\n						</div>\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span>非45度对角构图的可称为斜线构图法，可以达到事半功倍的效果。</span><br />\r\n<img id=\"aimg_273992\" src=\"http://img.bbs.lenovomobile.cn/forum/201611/06/191333fidfnummdd6dd5un.jpg.thumb.jpg\" /> \r\n						<div class=\"tip tip_4 aimg_tip\">\r\n							<div class=\"xs0\">\r\n								<p>\r\n									<strong>6.jpg</strong>\r\n								</p>\r\n								<p>\r\n									<br />\r\n								</p>\r\n								<p class=\"xg1\">\r\n									<span class=\"y xg1\">2016-11-6 19:13 上传</span><em>64.94 KB</em>\r\n								</p>\r\n							</div>\r\n							<div class=\"tip_horn\">\r\n							</div>\r\n						</div>\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n						<div align=\"center\">\r\n							人景融合构图法：点睛之笔\r\n						</div>\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span>大环境小人物，这样的照片构图凸显的是背景带来的视觉效果，人物是画面中的小小一个点缀，但是却是点睛之笔。<br />\r\n背景的空旷是必须的，当然，绝不允许有甲乙丙丁路人出现在画面中。</span><br />\r\n<span><br />\r\n</span><br />\r\n<img id=\"aimg_273993\" src=\"http://img.bbs.lenovomobile.cn/forum/201611/06/191333nhg6hc1xg6x1xpgc.jpg.thumb.jpg\" /> \r\n						<div class=\"tip tip_4 aimg_tip\">\r\n							<div class=\"xs0\">\r\n								<p>\r\n									<strong>7.jpg</strong>\r\n								</p>\r\n								<p>\r\n									<br />\r\n								</p>\r\n								<p class=\"xg1\">\r\n									<span class=\"y xg1\">2016-11-6 19:13 上传</span><em>77.01 KB</em>\r\n								</p>\r\n							</div>\r\n							<div class=\"tip_horn\">\r\n							</div>\r\n						</div>\r\n<span><br />\r\n</span><br />\r\n						<div class=\"viewthread_locked\">\r\n							ZUK946486，如果您要查看本帖隐藏内容请<a href=\"/forum.php?mod=post&amp;action=reply&amp;fid=39&amp;tid=317699\">回复</a>\r\n						</div>\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img id=\"aimg_273994\" src=\"http://img.bbs.lenovomobile.cn/forum/201611/06/191334dh939pxeuo9hdoh3.jpg.thumb.jpg\" /> \r\n						<div class=\"tip tip_4 aimg_tip\">\r\n							<div class=\"xs0\">\r\n								<p>\r\n									<strong>8.jpg</strong>\r\n								</p>\r\n								<p>\r\n									<br />\r\n								</p>\r\n								<p class=\"xg1\">\r\n									<span class=\"y xg1\">2016-11-6 19:13 